sp.p:
His steel was in debt;
it went o' the backside the
town.

Gentlemen, enough of this: it came
in too suddenly;
let it die as it was born, and,
I pray you, be better
acquainted.

This is but a custom in your tongue;
you
bear a graver purpose, I hope.

sp.l:
Quiet consummation have;
And renowned be thy grave!
Re-enter BELARIUS, with the body of CLOTEN.

And prove it in thy feeling. Heaven mend all!
Enter LUCIUS, IACHIMO, the Soothsayer, and other Roman Prisoners, guarded;
POSTHUMUS behind, and IMOGEN.
